    <main id="main" class="main">
      <article class="wrap">
        <div class="row prop-intro">
          <div class="column large-6">
            <h1>Share your debt story</h1>
            <h2>Write a letter to someone in trouble with money</h2>
            <p>Have you been in debt and successfully got out of it?</p>
            <p>If you have, you’ll know that problems with debt can make you feel very lonely.</p>
            <p>Getting a letter from a person who&rsquo;s been in a similar situation could make all the difference to someone struggling on their own.</p>
            <p>Do you have a debt story with a happy ending you could share with someone like you?</p>
            <p>[image showing an example letter]</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="column large-6">
            <h2>How it works</h2>
            <p>Tell us about a time when you had a debt problem. Big or small, it doesn&rsquo;t matter, we just want to hear about how you came through it.</p>
            <p>We&rsquo;ll match you with someone experiencing a similar problem right now who needs support.</p>
            <p>We&rsquo;ll tell you their first name, address, and a bit about the debt problem they are having at the moment.</p>
            <p>After that &mdash; you can write your first letter. </p>
            <p>If it&rsquo;s been years since you wrote a letter to anyone, we can help you get started with some examples, templates and writing tips.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="column large-6">
              <h2>What to write about</h2>
              <p>Tell the story of how you got into debt, and how you got out of it, in as much or as little detail as you feel is right. </p>
              <p>You don&rsquo;t have to give advice. It&rsquo;s not your job to get the person out of trouble.</p>
              <p>When you write to someone, you&rsquo;re reaching out to a person in a bad situation and giving them friendly support. </p>
              <p>Getting a handwritten letter through the post makes a nice change from bills and official letters. </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="column large-12 cta-area">
            <section>
              <h2>Tell your story, and help someone who feels alone</h2>
              <p>If you’ve had any kind of problem with debt and you’ve lived to tell the tale, your story could mean the world to someone just like you.</p>
              <p>Tell us your email address and we’ll find someone for your to write to.</p>
              <div class="page-1">
                <%= partial("future_brochure_signup_form", :locals => {:form_id => "join-form-1" }) %>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>

